Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Tor Connection Fails
# Restart Tor service
sudo systemctl restart tor

# Check Tor logs
sudo journalctl -u tor -n 50

# Verify Tor configuration
sudo tor --verify-config
Issue: Python Import Errors
# Install required packages
pip3 install requests beautifulsoup4 PySocks

# Verify installations
pip3 list | grep -E "requests|beautifulsoup4|PySocks"
Issue: SOCKS Proxy Errors
# Test SOCKS proxy directly
curl --socks5 127.0.0.1:9050 https://check.torproject.org/api/ip

# Check if port 9050 is listening
netstat -tlnp | grep 9050
Security Best Practices
Operational Security (OPSEC)
Always verify Tor connection before accessing dark web
Use random delays between automated requests (5-10 seconds minimum)
Maintain detailed logs for accountability and legal protection
Never access illegal content or engage in illegal activities
Encrypt sensitive data collected during research
Regular security scans to ensure system integrity
Legal Compliance Checklist
 Research purpose is educational/defensive
 All activities are documented
 No illegal content accessed
 Proper authorization obtained
 Incident response plan in place
 Legal counsel consulted if needed
